				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="category/foreign-policy/" title="View all posts in Foreign policy" rel="category tag">Foreign policy</a>			</span>
															<span class="sep"> | </span>
							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="tag/bush/" rel="tag">bush</a>, <a href="tag/civil-war/" rel="tag">civil war</a>, <a href="tag/cuba/" rel="tag">cuba</a>, <a href="tag/drones/" rel="tag">drones</a>, <a href="tag/fidel-castro/" rel="tag">fidel castro</a>, <a href="tag/foreign-policy-2/" rel="tag">foreign policy</a>, <a href="tag/income-tax/" rel="tag">income tax</a>, <a href="tag/indefinite-detention/" rel="tag">indefinite detention</a>, <a href="tag/lincoln/" rel="tag">lincoln</a>, <a href="tag/ndaa/" rel="tag">ndaa</a>, <a href="tag/obama/" rel="tag">Obama</a>, <a href="tag/operation-north-woods/" rel="tag">operation north woods</a>, <a href="tag/patriot-act/" rel="tag">Patriot act</a>, <a href="tag/rand-paul/" rel="tag">rand paul</a>, <a href="tag/rand-paul-drones/" rel="tag">rand paul drones</a>, <a href="tag/tsa/" rel="tag">TSA</a>, <a href="tag/war/" rel="tag">war</a>			</span>
						
									<span class="sep"> | </span>
						<span class="comments-link"><a href="2013/03/11/beyond-the-drones-what-americans-should-consider-before-supporting-any-kill/#respond" title="Comment on Beyond the Drones: What Americans Should Consider Before Supporting Any Kill"><span class="leave-reply">Leave a reply</span></a></span>
			
